#

Tofu Salad

10 min
$10
350 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

Soy

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianVeganGluten-Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main Dish

Tags:

HealthyQuickFresh

Description

A refreshing and protein-packed salad featuring crispy tofu, fresh vegetables, and a zesty dressing.

Ingredients

  • firm tofu: 1 block (14 oz)
  • mixed salad greens: 4 cups
  • cherry tomatoes: 1 cup
  • cucumber: 1 medium
  • avocado: 1
  • olive oil: 3 tablespoons
  • soy sauce: 2 tablespoons
  • lemon juice: 1 tablespoon
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
